text: Liane Sorenson (born August 13, 1947) is an American politician who served in the Delaware House of Representatives from the 12th district from 1993 to 1995 and in the Delaware Senate from the 6th district from 1995 to 2013. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Delaware House of Representatives Category:Delaware state senators Category:Delaware Republicans
title: Liane Sorenson
